            <h3 class="heading-92913 text-black text-center">What Customer Saying...</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="mb-4 mb-lg-0 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="testimony-39291">
              <blockquote>
<p>We have a Dual rate Energy tariff with Outfox the Market. Night time usage is avering 40% of total usage per month for the last few years</p>
              </blockquote>
              <div class="d-flex vcard align-items-center">
                <div class="pic mr-3">
                  <img src="{% static 'images/person_3_sq.jpg' %}" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                  <strong class="d-block">John Doe</strong>
                  <span>CEO and Co-Founder</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 mb-lg-0 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="testimony-39291">
              <blockquote>
                <p>2 dates missed by SSE to fit smart meter. No show by fitter . 2 times I agreed set times email when coming they have changed times . </p>
              </blockquote>
              <div class="d-flex vcard align-items-center">
                <div class="pic mr-3">
                  <img src="{% static 'images/person_4_sq.jpg' %}" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                  <strong class="d-block">John Doe</strong>
                  <span>CEO and Co-Founder</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 mb-lg-0 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="testimony-39291">
              <blockquote>
                <p>I was living in a house that have a normal meters for electricity and gas.Then I changed to smart meters. my god my bills shot up so high.</p>
              </blockquote>
              <div class="d-flex vcard align-items-center">
                <div class="pic mr-3">
                  <img src="{% static 'images/person_3_sq.jpg' %}" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="text">
